actions.message:
Hello ${member} , Welcome to ${tempVars("ServerInfo")}! 
Here's a list of commands.

Fun Commands:-

!snowball - Throw a snowball at somebody!
!trump    - Generate a Donald Trump quote!
!fact     - Grabs a random fact.
!8ball    - Ask the 8ball!
!emolets [text] - Change your words into emojis!
!leftexit - Tag someone with this, and it'll generate leftexit meme
!sign     - Danger sign on the tagged person.
!dadjoke  - Grabs a funny joke lol
!wasted   - Puts a wasted image over a mentioned person

======================================================================

Music Commands:-

!play - Play a song!
!skip - Skip the current song.
!pause - Pause the video.
!resume - Resume the video.
!volume - Change volume.
!connect - Connect me to the voice channel.
!disconnect - Remove me from the voice channel.

==================================================================
Reputation Commands:-

!rep [@user] - Reps a user with one point
!me - Shows your warning and rep points
!set_r_points - Staff only.
!you [@user] Shows another persons warning/rep points

==================================================================
Other Commands:-

!verify - Verification system
!warnings - View warnings
!feedback - Give feedback to the bot developer.
!bugreport - Sends a DM to the bot developer for a bug.
!servers - Shows main servers for the bot
!mydata - The bot sends you a DM of what the bot stores about you.
!changelog - View current bot updates.
==================================================================
Support Help:-

!ticket - Makes a ticket
!closeticket - Closes the current ticket
==================================================================
**STAFF:
Do !staff-help for staff commands.



If you need any assistance contact ${tempVars("ServerInfo")}'s Staff
